## Accessibility Requirements

- [ ] Color contrast meets WCAG AA (4.5:1 for body text, 3:1 for large text)
- [ ] All interactive elements have visible focus states
- [ ] Form fields have associated labels (not just placeholder text)
- [ ] Error messages are programmatically associated with fields
- [ ] Touch targets are at least 44×44px on mobile
- [ ] No information conveyed by color alone
- [ ] [Any project-specific requirements from elicitation]

---

